title: 8 Miles Under Water
info:
The depth of sea
You are surrounded by walls of darkness. Thousand tons of frigid water are liying above you. You feel the overcoming exhaustion - and then you hear the call of the Nymph Queen.

I fear that song didn't come out as good as i hoped... It was done with ST3, and i better should use my Easytracker.
